</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_385_r2l35"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / als etlıch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> / den Mertein des Nıkel Erharts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r2l36">knecht bey eẅch ʒu fenknuſſ bracht Vnd vns ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r2l37">haben . daʒ Jr eẅch darinne freẅntlıch vnd gutwıllıg beweıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r2l38">habt / Des <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> weıſheıt mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r2l39"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> Morıcʒen Awracher <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r2l40"><expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> / Dem wır befolhen haben mıt ew <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu reden . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r2l41">wır eẅr <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> <expan>fleıſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / was <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> vnſer <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_386" id="192r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l1">dıſem male in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅch werbe daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l2">Jm des <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben / vnd eẅch darinn <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ſo freẅntlıch vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l3">fürderlıch beweıſen vnd darcʒu tun wellet als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_386_r1l4"><expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol getrawen vnd eẅch vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey vns <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun </ab>
